{"tid":1293771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日77 班毅進仔忍唔撚住俾晒料文宣做野","createTime":"2019-07-07T16:46:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T17:38:31.000Z","uid":70888,"like":102,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"675235ace438072d1f45358d6ab593b30cf48d56","tid":1293771,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:46:15.000Z","msg":"感謝每一位真香港人，大家先休息，聽日一齊幫手文宣<br />\n<br />\n1。男黑警騎住女市民落地<br />\n2。主動撩人隻抽<br />\n3。話執行期間唔需要委任證都得<br />\n4。話唔俾市民走<br />\n5。無理拘捕示威者<br />\n6。女便衣警影人大頭再打人，跟住警犬護送佢走<br />\n7。的士司機死火，無理拘捕<br />\n<br />\n仲有大量不能盡錄，聽日會有更多人提供到影片同相<br />\n<br />\n毅進仔之前仲想洗底扮好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過由屯公到今日77，毅進仔既爛仔性格出晒黎，垃圾露晒底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地要係依個時間凝聚返力量，亦都將黑警惡行廣傳<br />\n<br />\n同埋記住五大訴求，仲有援助被捕義士"},{"pid":"01db72725c21d94e132691c051e63f7def368b32","tid":1293771,"uid":177338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:47:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6a2dfb01cfa7ada5ed75642865d967d481ba1ea3","tid":1293771,"uid":5650,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:47:33.000Z","msg":"成理前線狗都好似有精神病<br />\n明明無人都仲係到推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ae99102131183b109f4d10d10e7296d03ef8f36","tid":1293771,"uid":204352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:47:59.000Z","msg":"狗改不了吃屎<br />\n叫啲狗用抽水馬桶屙屎有閪用咩"},{"pid":"1d415c23cc446e4bd3b986ab0615b3597f3c2643","tid":1293771,"uid":46603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:48:02.000Z","msg":"佢地eq 太低 忍唔到"},{"pid":"d6502c4f2fcab3d133f5ab36f19a0a3cbc48c3e1","tid":1293771,"uid":249703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:49:01.000Z",